  title: "MATRIX Element P2 Speaker Amplifier",
  handle:
    "matrix-element-p2-power-amplifier-class-d-amplification-speaker-amplifier",
  description:
    '<p><img alt="" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0013/3896/6076/files/DM_20240326161501_009.png?v=1711440965" data-mce-src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0013/3896/6076/files/DM_20240326161501_009.png?v=1711440965" data-mce-fragment="1"><img alt="" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0013/3896/6076/files/DM_20240326161500_001.jpg?v=1711440971" data-mce-src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0013/3896/6076/files/DM_20240326161500_001.jpg?v=1711440971" data-mce-fragment="1"></p>\n<h2>A powerful fulcrum of your Hi-Fi system</h2>\n<div data-scroll-reveal-complete="true" data-scroll-reveal-initialized="true" data-scroll-reveal-id="1" data-scroll-reveal="" class="content-1 content-2 no-padding">\n<div class="container-xxl dec">\n<p>Continuing with the element sieries family design language, the element P2 power amplifier inherits the simple and modern design. With Class-D amplification technology, providing plenty of power to various bookshelf speakers and floorstanding speakers. Let your whole audio system perform better than ever.</p>\n<p><img alt="" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0013/3896/6076/files/DM_20240326161500_002.png?v=1711440971" data-mce-src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0013/3896/6076/files/DM_20240326161500_002.png?v=1711440971"></p>\n<h2>The outside matches the inside</h2>\n<div data-scroll-reveal-complete="true" data-scroll-reveal-initialized="true" data-scroll-reveal-id="2" data-scroll-reveal="" class="content-1 content-2 no-padding">\n<div class="container-xxl dec">\n<p>The appearance of element P2 matches with the element product line from Matrix, which looks elegant at every angle. It integrates with your home furniture organically. Audio equipment is no longer a cold and heartless block, with an element P2, it is so easy to build an ideal sound system with both perfect sound and beautiful look.</p>\n<p><img alt="" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0013/3896/6076/files/DM_20240326161500_003.png?v=1711440971" data-mce-src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0013/3896/6076/files/DM_20240326161500_003.png?v=1711440971"></p>\n<h2>Multiple input methods</h2>\n<div class="content-1 content-5">\n<div class="container-xxl item" data-scroll-reveal="" data-scroll-reveal-id="3" data-scroll-reveal-initialized="true" data-scroll-reveal-complete="true">\n<div class="info">\n<p>An excellent power amplifier is essential for flexible input methods. The element P2 is equipped with RCA and XLR input ports. No matter your front-end device has balanced or single-ended output, delivers the original signal of music to the amplifier authentically and accurately.</p>\n<p><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0013/3896/6076/files/DM_20240326161500_004.png?v=1711440971" alt="" data-mce-src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0013/3896/6076/files/DM_20240326161500_004.png?v=1711440971"></p>\n<h4>Stereo mode</h4>\n<div class="item">\n<div>\n<p>In stereo mode, the element P2 provides 230W output power to each channel at 4 ohms load, drives bookshelf speakers or small floorstanding speakers effortlessly. The sound will take you to the real stage, keep every detail of the music, fully interpret the meaning of Hi-Fi.</p>\n<p><img alt="" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0013/3896/6076/files/DM_20240326161501_005.png?v=1711440971"></p>\n<h4>Double power on mono mode</h4>\n<div class="content-7 content-6">\n<div data-scroll-reveal-complete="true" data-scroll-reveal-initialized="true" data-scroll-reveal-id="4" data-scroll-reveal="" class="container-xxl wrapper">\n<div class="item">\n<div>\n<p>With two element P2 which are configured to mono mode, each amplifier works with one speaker, you\'ll get 850W output power from each channel at 4 ohms load. Unleash the full potential of your speaker system, even with low-sensitivity floor-standing speakers.</p>\n<p><img alt="" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0013/3896/6076/files/DM_20240326161501_006.png?v=1711440972"></p>\n<h2>Fine music starts on a "trigger"</h2>\n<div class="content-1 content-5">\n<div data-scroll-reveal-complete="true" data-scroll-reveal-initialized="true" data-scroll-reveal-id="5" data-scroll-reveal="" class="container-xxl item">\n<div class="info">\n<p>Techniques make people lazier. When the element P2 is connected to a front-end device which has trigger ports, the unit will enter working status immediately from standby mode without manual operations.</p>\n<h2>Brilliant connectors from WBT</h2>\n<div class="info">\n<p>With the newly added "moment of force indicator" to the hand-tightened part of WBT-0708 Cu, the pole terminals and the spades of speaker wires are protected effectively. The terminal uses hollow design, the conductors are gold-plated on pure copper and anti-oxidation treated. To effortlessly achieve a low impedance connection with high reliability, and easily cope with instantaneous high current. Always ready to provide sufficient power for magnificent music.</p>\n<p><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0013/3896/6076/files/DM_20240326161501_007.png?v=1711440971" alt="" data-mce-fragment="1" data-mce-src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0013/3896/6076/files/DM_20240326161501_007.png?v=1711440971"><img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0013/3896/6076/files/DM_20240326161501_008.png?v=1711440971" alt="" data-mce-fragment="1" data-mce-src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0013/3896/6076/files/DM_20240326161501_008.png?v=1711440971"><br></p>\n<h2>Ceramic Ball Vibration Buffer</h2>\n<div class="content-1 content-5">\n<div data-scroll-reveal-complete="true" data-scroll-reveal-initialized="true" data-scroll-reveal-id="7" data-scroll-reveal="" class="container-xxl item">\n<div class="info">\n<p>The element P2 is equipped with CBVB pads. The core of CBVB is made of ceramic balls and silicone rubber. There are 6 ceramic balls in each pad to minimize the noises caused by mechanical vibration. The transparency of the sound is further improved, creating a wide and clear sound stage for you.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>',
